{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/compound-assignment-with-augmented-addition","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Slozena Dodela sa Uvecanim Sabiranjem","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U programiranju je uobicajeno koristiti dodelu da bi se promenio sadrzaj promenljive. Zapamtite da se sve sa desne strane znaka jednakosti prvo izracuna, pa mozemo napisati:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">myVar = myVar + 5;\n</code></pre>\n<p>da dodamo <code>5</code> na <code>myVar</code>. Posto je ovo vrlo cest obrazac, postoje operatori koji matematicku operaciju i dodelu obavljaju u jednom koraku.</p>\n<p>Jedan od tih operatora je <code>+=</code>.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let myVar = 1;\nmyVar += 5;\nconsole.log(myVar);\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>6</code> ce biti ispisano u konzoli.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244af","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Promenite dodele vrednosti za <code>a</code>, <code>b</code> i <code>c</code> tako da koriste <code>+=</code> operator.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16661,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/compound-assignment-with-augmented-addition"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"let a = 3;\nlet b = 17;\nlet c = 12;\n\n// Only change code below this line\na = a + 12;\nb = 9 + b;\nc = c + 7;","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>a</code> treba da bude jednak <code>15</code>.</